{"title":"(Vue) Emit 向外層傳遞事件","uid":"a5045e59613c76e310a3e10bea8114be","slug":"Emit-向外層傳遞事件","date":"2021-08-14T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-07-29T14:36:56.235Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Emit-向外層傳遞事件.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<aside>\n💡 可以不用一定要傳遞數值，可以只傳送事件\n</aside>\n\n<ul>\n<li>定義外層事件</li>\n<li>定義內層事件且將 emit 做命名</li>\n<li>在 html 標籤加上綁上事件 <code>v-on:內層 emit 名稱 = &quot;外層事件&quot;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"Emit-來觸發外部事件\"><a href=\"#Emit-來觸發外部事件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Emit 來觸發外部事件\"></a>Emit 來觸發外部事件</h1><ul>\n<li>先定義外層接收的方法</li>\n<li>定義內層的 $emit 觸發方法</li>\n<li>使用 <code>v-on</code> 的方式觸發外層方法（口訣：前內、後外）<ul>\n<li>元件內層的 $emit 會指向到外層的 html 標籤上</li>\n<li>html 標籤會根據 <code>v-on:emit-num</code> 所綁定的事件做觸發</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BiymkjR.png\" alt=\"傳遞事件流程圖\"><br>傳遞事件流程圖</p>\n<p>完整程式碼：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;\n  &#123;&#123; num &#125;&#125;\n  &lt;button-counter v-on:emit-num&#x3D;&quot;addNum&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;button-counter&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-jsx\" data-language=\"jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">const app &#x3D; Vue.createApp(&#123;\n    data() &#123;\n      return &#123;\n        num: 0,\n      &#125;;\n    &#125;,\n    methods: &#123;\n      addNum()&#123;\n        console.log(&#39;觸發 addNum&#39;)\n        this.num++\n      &#125;\n    &#125;\n  &#125;);\n\n  app.component(&#39;button-counter&#39;, &#123;\n    methods: &#123;\n      click()&#123;\n        console.log(&#39;觸發 $emit&#39;)\n        this.$emit(&#39;emit-num&#39;)\n      &#125;\n    &#125;,\n    template: &#96;&lt;button type&#x3D;&quot;button&quot; \n    @click&#x3D;&quot;click&quot;&gt; add &lt;&#x2F;button&gt;&#96;\n  &#125;);\n\n  app.mount(&#39;#app&#39;);</code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"傳遞資料狀態\"><a href=\"#傳遞資料狀態\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"傳遞資料狀態\"></a>傳遞資料狀態</h1><p>將內部資料透過事件渲染到畫面上</p>\n<ul>\n<li>先定義外層接收的方法</li>\n<li>定義內層的 $emit 觸發方法</li>\n<li>使用 <code>v-on</code> 的方式觸發外層方法（口訣：前內、後外）<ul>\n<li>元件內層的 $emit 會指向到外層的 html 標籤上</li>\n<li>html 標籤會根據 <code>v-on:emit-num</code> 所綁定的事件做觸發</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sQFAonC.png\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"命名限制\"><a href=\"#命名限制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"命名限制\"></a>命名限制</h1><aside>\n💡 因為 html 內有規定，標籤屬性都只能使用小寫 !\n\n</aside>\n\n<p>props 內的資料假使命名為 <code>this.$emit(&#39;emitText&#39;)</code><br>直接新增此名稱上 html 時是無法被讀取到的，可以改用：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>html 屬性改為：<code>@emit-text</code></li>\n<li>$emit 名稱改為：<code>this.$emit(&#39;emit-text&#39;)</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Demo:</p>\n<iframe height=\"300\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Emit 向外層傳遞事件\" src=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/embed/eYWqrRa?default-tab=html%2Cresult&theme-id=dark\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/pen/eYWqrRa\">\n  Emit 向外層傳遞事件</a> by Michael Luo (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo\">@michael-luo</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>","text":" 💡 可以不用一定要傳遞數值，可以只傳送事件 定義外層事件 定義內層事件且將 emit 做命名 在 html 標籤加上綁上事件 v-on:內層 emit 名稱 = &quot;外層事件&quot; Emit 來觸發外部事件 先定義外層接收的方法 定義內層的 $emit 觸發方法 ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Emit-%E4%BE%86%E8%A7%B8%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Emit 來觸發外部事件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%82%B3%E9%81%9E%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">傳遞資料狀態</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">命名限制</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"(Vue) Emits 驗證","uid":"1595e531dec8403b66a8d4d6374df417","slug":"Emits-驗證","date":"2021-08-15T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-07-29T14:36:56.235Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Emits-驗證.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"當我們要把內層的數值指向化定義到外層時，不是一定要重新 Methods，可以直接寫在 html 上 在 template 內加上 $emit 並且帶上事件名稱以及參數，即可觸發 在 html 上的元件內加上事件（口訣：前內($emit 的名稱 add)、後外（’addNum()’...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.8k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"(Vue) Props 向內層元件傳遞資料狀態","uid":"246e2d523d5abb09b5ea4ba84af8f20e","slug":"Props-向內層元件傳遞資料狀態","date":"2021-08-13T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-07-29T14:36:56.242Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Props-向內層元件傳遞資料狀態.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"靜態資源傳入圖片連結範例： 在建立好的 app.component 方法內建立 props 變數且帶入一個陣列 array，且新增資料 url 將 template 帶上 &lt;img&gt; 標籤，且使用 v-bind:src=&quot;url&quot; 在 html 內...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/categori